  "title": "Service Restaurant Crew",
  "description": "<p><h3><strong></strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Guide the Flow:</strong> Steer daily floor operations with precision. Connect the kitchen and dining teams to create seamless, timely service.</p></li><li><p><strong>Set the Standard:</strong> Be a visible presence on the floor. Lead by example in guest care, cleanliness, and maintaining our high-energy atmosphere.</p></li><li><p><strong>Uplift the Team:</strong> Mentor and coach junior staff. Foster a supportive, positive culture where everyone is encouraged to grow and succeed.</p></li><li><p><strong>Solve with Grace:</strong> Anticipate service challenges and resolve them with poise. Your focus is always on protecting and enhancing the guest experience.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Have 1-2 years of experience in a fast-paced, full-service restaurant.</p></li></ul></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>EA Personnel R22110043 Tan Eng Kang</p><p>EA License 21C0430 A Dreamworks Company Pte Ltd</p>",
